J. E. EDGE, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 15364. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. May 20, 1955. J. E. Edge, in pro. per. James W. Dorsey, U. S. Atty., Harvey H. Tisinger, Asst. U. S. Atty., Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before RIVES and CAMERON, Circuit Judges, and DAWKINS, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is Affirmed.
